import { TrendingUp, TrendingDown, Thermometer, Droplets, Wind, Sun, AlertTriangle, Download, BarChart3, Zap, Satellite, MapPin, Calendar, Loader } from 'lucide-react'; import { BarChart, Bar, XAxis, YAxis, CartesianGrid, Tooltip, ResponsiveContainer, LineChart, Line, PieChart, Pie, Cell } from 'recharts'; import { useState, useEffect } from 'react'; import GIBSService from '../services/api/gibsService'; const ResultsDisplay = ({ results }) => { const { probabilities, location, date, summary, historicalData } = results; const [satelliteImage, setSatelliteImage] = useState(null); const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false); const loadSatelliteImage = async (condition) => { try { setLoading(true); const bbox = { north: location.lat + 2, south: location.lat - 2, east: location.lon + 2, west: location.lon - 2 }; const imageUrl = await GIBSService.getImageryUrl(condition, new Date(date), bbox); setSatelliteImage(imageUrl); } catch (error) { console.error('Error loading satellite image:', error); // You might want to add error handling UI here } finally { setLoading(false); } }; // Prepare data for charts const probabilityData = [ { name: 'Hot (>35°C)', value: probabilities.hot, color: '#ef4444' }, { name: 'Cold (<5°C)', value: probabilities.cold, color: '#3b82f6' }, { name: 'Wet (>10mm)', value: probabilities.wet, color: '#06b6d4' }, { name: 'Windy (>10m/s)', value: probabilities.windy, color: '#6b7280' }, { name: 'Uncomfortable', value: probabilities.uncomfortable, color: '#f59e0b' } ]; const monthlyData = historicalData?.monthly || []; const COLORS = ['#ef4444', '#3b82f6', '#06b6d4', '#6b7280', '#f59e0b']; const getProbabilityLevel = (value) => { if (value >= 70) return { level: 'High', color: 'text-red-600', bg: 'bg-red-50' }; if (value >= 40) return { level: 'Medium', color: 'text-yellow-600', bg: 'bg-yellow-50' }; return { level: 'Low', color: 'text-green-600', bg: 'bg-green-50' }; }; const formatDate = (dateString) => { return new Date(dateString).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' }); }; return (
